pageContext.claim: “And look at what we've done in less than three years. I mean, look at the progress you've made. Everything is historic, meaning it's never happened in the history of our country, what we've done.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump has a habit of saying “everything is historic” when it isn't. The economy has continued to grow under the Trump administration, even breaking record at times, but to suggest every economic statistic is “historic” is flat out false.
